* Per podcast setting to ignore the last modified response from the server.
* Do not remove the reply in PodcastEpisode::downloadSuccessful because
  it's still needed. PodcastEpisode::cleanDownload will take care of that
  later.
* Added config option to ignore not modified responses from the server.
* Updated documentation.


Oct 16, 2008 - John Schember <john@nachtimwald.com>

* Check last modified header when downloading RSS feeds and do not download
  the feed if it has not been modified since it was last checked.
* New database format.
* Framework to update the database for when new features are added.
* Opts displays name of the executable instead of the application's internal
  name.
* Correctly sets file name when dealing with redirects.
* Re-structure some client code.
* User agent is set for downloads. Server will see the name of this application
  as the downloading client.
* Fixed a typo.


